data.description:
Bar Manager – Wembley Stadium: 
Wembley Royal Suite (the most exclusive offering from Club Wembley) and The One Twenty Club (delivers the highest level of luxury)

Being promoted to Bar Manager within ‘The Royal Wembley Suite’, gave me the opportunity to hone my management skills, coaching an extensive team of between 10-20 staff members, who were tasked with the responsibility of providing a high-quality service to a sophisticated mix of people. In this role I prided myself on creating an exceptional working environment amongst my team. Our key focus was to provide an impeccable service for those fortunate enough to be part of a match/event days within The Royal Wembley Suite. As the first port of call for any customer queries or issues, I developed an understanding nature, as well as the ability to take on-board the opinions of others and showing compassion in resolving any issues put to me.

My key take aways from this role are the skills I gained related to the importance of the customers experience and relationship building.
data.title: Bar Manager

data.description:
Due to the quality of relationships, I built with key accounts, I was promoted to a Business Development Role. The experience I gained as Warehouse Manager placed me in a unique position to be able to understand potential frustrations, and expectations of our target audience.

data.headline: Account Manager - Pentesec | Cybersecurity Sales.
data.summary:
Pentesec's SOC services are managed within our 24/7/365 UK based SOC. Diligently overseen by a seasoned team of analysts, security engineers, IR specialists, support staff and threat hunters. Pentesecs SOC delivers a variety of services that can cover the entire incident management process, relying on automation to correlate vast amounts of logs and security event data, before passing the results on for human analysis, if required.

Our SOC services consist of Managed SIEM, Managed EDR, Managed Vulnerability Management, Managed Microsoft Sentinel & Managed Microsoft Defender As A Service.
